Should be transportable over UDP

Message types
  Informational
    Sights, sounds, status, etc
  Request/renew/cancel subscription
    e.g. to image stream
  Command
    Move, look at, etc

All messages should contain
  Channel ID
  Ordering value (so when receiving contradictory information, newer can take precedence)

Encryption/authentication is outside the scope for now

This may map nicely to
http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constrained_Application_Protocol
CoAP has an 'observe' extension: https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-core-observe-04
